- Use the `create` tool for new files (Models.cs, ClinicService.cs, new page razor files, AGENTS.md).
- Delete template pages (Counter.razor, Weather.razor, Auth.razor) using `bash rm`.
- Make sure the project builds successfully at the end.
"}

